commit.message:
Created DescriptionFragment
DescriptionFragment displays the event description using ExpandableTextView library. New drawables are for the fragments ImageButton.

Created detail_page subdirectory
This directory will house all code for the Event Details Page. Already moved DTLFragment and EventDetailsActivity to this directory.
Added shadows in Event Detail Page

Began revamping Event Details Page
Began redoing the UI for the Event Details Page. A new EventDetailsActivity has been created along with DTLFragment. DTLFragment (Date-Time-Location) handles display of required event info using a ListView, dtl_item.xml is the ListView's item xml. Old code has been renamed with the _old suffix attached.

Moved code from onRestart to onResume in HomePageActivity
This fixes a bug where the events weren't being refreshed if an orientation change happened in the previous activity.
made HomePageActivity:buildMap static
Moved initial server request to SplashActivity, requests afterward are still handled by HomePageActivity
Created SplashActivity and a background_splash drawable which will be used for loading screen.
EventDetailsActivity now grabs data from server instead from AllEventsFragment. This is for future database features.
Fixed bug where Views were duplicated when orientation changes
HomePage Activity now correctly refreshes events when you signup/unsign from one.

Changed the way events are saved
Since ServerAPI now works as intended, events don't need to be replicated on the local device anymore. Instead, the event's key and name are stored in a local JSON file and the rest of the data is pulled from the server.
Also added a Map Marker which will mark the events location.
Also renamed MainActivity to HomePageActivity, this is in preparation for a loading screen activity.
Made ServerAPI asynchronous so MainActivity now has to wait for ServerAPI to complete its request before retrieving data.
Fixed Attending tab
ViewPager without different pages
Event descriptions are now properly taken from server and displayed
Made Map work properly
Added BottomBarFragment. Also added get request code.
Added map. Map moves to current location after a delay.
Added tab's to action bar
Initial commit
